  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a kadhai over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the grated carrot and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced mushroom and cook until it is tender.",
    "Add the rice and stir to combine with the vegetables.",
    "Add the cayenne pepper, soy sauce, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
